Package sph.vaadin.ui.svg

Contains Vaadin based SVG UI components and related resources.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SvgDots.DotListener
    SvgDotsListener interface for listening to SvgDots.Dot events fired by an SvgDots component.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SvgDots
    SvgDots Component draws colored circles (dots) horizontally to an SVG canvas.
    SvgDots.Dot
    Dot contains all the required information about a single SVG dot in SvgDots component.
    SvgDotsState
    SvgDotsState object is a shared state object for SvgDots component.
